// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1511 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: cbfc4d00-ae87-5708-843c-51873bd6a3ba

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*")
